3T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"咁當初點解要攬炒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:57:27.000Z","msg":"講緊武肺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"因為佢地無林奠啫, 整個林奠比佢地嘆下, 就知咩叫生活艱難<br />\n乜撚都唔做, 淨係識為自己利益搞政治小動作"},{"pid":"57733c03069988d752f288a05e46e55233f6adb8","tid":2200533,"uid":264783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3520e52e8eca4624c4723570abef64b997c15e1e","tid":2200533,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">一齊google畀零分比香島中學 等啲家長揀嘅時候會考慮清楚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n之前我地<span class=\"purple\"><strong>過百留言一一被delete</strong></span>，估計被google評為無效，請繼續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FrpGUKs&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513RyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=b5704926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/rpGUKs</a><br />\n天水圍香島中學<br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FeNAKtm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513RyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=efcb3ba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/eNAKtm</a><br />\n將軍澳香島中學 <br />\n<a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg.co%2Fkgs%2FC9Vm&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513RyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=107eaec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://g.co/kgs/C9Vm</a></span>Z3<br />\n<br />\n留言:<br />\n事件一<br />\n校方帶頭將政治帶入校園，一名教師懷疑在音樂考試時未有禁止學生演奏「不恰當歌曲」而不獲續約。<br />\n<br />\n事件二<br />\n香島中學正校關注組指，9月7日一名中四學生突然被校長及訓導主任召回學校會面，校方指該名同學在網上溝通軟件Microsoft Team的簡介上填寫了抗爭口號，因而作出處分，包括立即停學一個星期，並向教育局通報。校方向該名學生表示，若然希望保留學位則需要記兩個大過，及警告再有發現參與社會運動，將會立即開除學籍。<br />\n<br />\n關注組成員又提到，校方曾多次警告該名學生不要參與社會活動，否則後果自負等；又指校方「敕令停課」的處分嚴重，形容是關注組成立後至今最嚴重的處分，指校方從未有處分關注組的成員或對抗校方的同學，故對校方處分「平平無奇」的學生感到詫異。"},{"pid":"2ad0eb22e13d3f3e3588ccbe617a4a9b8f8d3707","tid":2200533,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"係, 比啲掌聲自己"},{"pid":"c202a669e2e050eff760e64504424a0237e35bfe","tid":2200533,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"出下街喇，放寬左限聚令經濟報仇式上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps 原先係限聚令下經濟仲係好好"},{"pid":"eb07a04d45a89c2efb7f26922b15647521e2b698","tid":2200533,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"無所謂，打世界波"},{"pid":"d16b73a888fe8ced9583d63567cbb730f12a7f3a","tid":2200533,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"留咁深水埗上海北京海南呀！<br />\n香港就是小漁村！"}]}